SELECT
    a.loket_id,
    a.pelayanan_id,
    a.tgl,
    '' as nosurat,
    c.pusk,
    a.puskesmas,
    a.pustu,
    c.kop_line1,
    c.kop_line2,
    c.kop_line3,
    c.kop_gambar,
    d.dokter,
    d.nip,
    a.nama,
    a.tgl_lahir,
    a.sex,
    a.usia,
    a.alamat,
    a.rw,
    a.rt,
    e.nama_kabupaten,
    f.nama_kecamatan,
    g.nama_kelurahan,
    concat(b.sistole,'/',b.diastole,' mmHg') as tensi,
    concat(b.nadi, ' x/mnt') as nadi,
    concat(b.suhu, ' Celcius') as suhu,
    concat(b.rr, ' x/mnt') as pernafasan,
    concat(b.tbne, ' Cm') as tb,
    concat(b.bbne, ' Kg') as bb

FROM pendaftaran a
LEFT JOIN pemeriksaan b ON a.pelayanan_id = b.pelayanan_id
LEFT JOIN puskesmas c ON a.puskesmas = c.pusk_id
LEFT JOIN master_dokter d ON CAST(a.dokter AS INTEGER) = d.dokter_id  -- ✅ GANTI INI
LEFT JOIN m_kabupaten e ON a.kabkota = e.mst_kabupaten_id
LEFT JOIN m_kecamatan f ON a.kecamatan = f.mst_kecamatan_id
LEFT JOIN m_kelurahan g ON a.kelurahan = g.mst_kelurahan_id
name: administrasi
